{"tid":1383201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國勢力呢，金主呢 每人五千蚊呀大佬","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T00:22:45.000Z","uid":135867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e8f042fa08dc11a7b14f95b1e162452ab9f46b","tid":1383201,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"班撚屌 成日話遊行有錢收係咪傻撚咗呀<br />\n<br />\n飯都未食得飽仲要買GEAR<br />\n係咪有金主呀係咪有外國勢力呀<br />\n快啲出嚟啦求下你<br />\n<br />\n班仆街，遊行之前同遊行之後有餐食。<br />\n我哋遊完行又要驚畀人捉呢樣嗰樣返到屋企又要同人鬧交， 又話趕你出門口<br />\n<br />\n而家買gear買到冇曬錢飯都冇得食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有外國勢力同金主唔該你快撚啲出嚟啦"},{"pid":"7ec7ed35abc32a4f4033e3cd45992417b9496fd2","tid":1383201,"uid":219814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9975a0c5bbba2628a3bf489909df0a7e521bed6d","tid":1383201,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8876fc543362b8250ee1b2601049daa516c9ba70","tid":1383201,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}